!! Snapshot limits

<div class="rr-input-row">
	Max manual snapshots per tiddler:
	<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/rimir/minver/max-manual" tag="input" default="3" class="rr-input" style="width:60px"/>
	<span class="rr-muted">(user-created snapshots)</span>
</div>

<div class="rr-input-row">
	Max auto snapshots per tiddler:
	<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/rimir/minver/max-auto" tag="input" default="3" class="rr-input" style="width:60px"/>
	<span class="rr-muted">(created on save)</span>
</div>

!! Scope

<div class="rr-input-row">
	Auto-snapshot filter:
	<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/rimir/minver/scope-filter" tag="input" default="[all[]]" class="rr-input"/>
</div>
<div class="rr-muted">Only tiddlers matching this filter will get auto-snapshots on save. Default: <code>[all[]]</code> (all tiddlers).</div>

!! Storage

<div class="rr-input-row">
	<$checkbox tiddler="$:/config/rimir/minver/auto-to-storage" field="text" checked="yes" unchecked="no" default="no">
		Persist auto-snapshots to browser storage
	</$checkbox>
</div>

<%if [[$:/config/rimir/minver/auto-to-storage]get[text]match[yes]] %>
<div class="rr-callout rr-callout-warning">
	⚠ Auto-snapshots will be saved to browser localStorage. This uses more space (~5-10MB limit shared with TiddlyWiki). Monitor usage in the [[manager|$:/plugins/rimir/minver/manager]].
</div>
<%endif%>

<div class="rr-input-row" style="margin-top:12px">
	Browser storage usage: <strong><$text text={{{ [[$:/temp/minver/storage-usage]get[text]else[calculating...]] }}}/></strong>
</div>

!! Change-groups

<div class="rr-input-row">
	Max change-groups in storage:
	<$edit-text tiddler="$:/config/rimir/minver/max-groups" tag="input" default="10" class="rr-input" style="width:60px"/>
	<span class="rr-muted">(oldest evicted when exceeded)</span>
</div>

